WEBVTT

00:05.040 --> 00:05.049
.

00:05.120 --> 00:06.089
MALE NARRATOR:

00:05.209 --> 00:06.089
Previously on Debris...

00:07.110 --> 00:08.109
BRYAN: When was the last time

00:07.110 --> 00:08.109
you saw your father?

00:08.119 --> 00:10.210
In the morgue.

00:08.119 --> 00:10.210
Hed already taken his own life.

00:10.210 --> 00:12.130
I havent really gotten

00:10.210 --> 00:12.130
over that.

00:12.130 --> 00:14.050
Hes alive.

00:12.130 --> 00:14.050
He wrote the whole playbook.

00:14.060 --> 00:16.170
BRYAN:

00:14.060 --> 00:16.170
This is gonna affect Finola.

00:16.170 --> 00:18.000
Youve got his eyes.

00:18.010 --> 00:19.089
WOMAN:

00:18.010 --> 00:19.089
These men took my father.

00:19.089 --> 00:20.210
FINOLA:

00:19.089 --> 00:20.210
You gotta give me something.

00:20.210 --> 00:22.160
FERRIS:

00:20.210 --> 00:22.160
Did you do what I asked?

00:22.170 --> 00:23.199
I cant trust Ferris.

00:23.210 --> 00:25.070
And you cant trust Maddox.

00:25.079 --> 00:27.079
BRYAN: This man saved my life.

00:27.089 --> 00:30.030
Finola, hey. I will get

00:27.089 --> 00:30.030
what I need out of him.

00:30.039 --> 00:31.190
(power surges)

00:31.199 --> 00:33.149
They found your father.

00:35.210 --> 00:38.140
(woman panting)

00:53.140 --> 00:55.090
(panting continues)

01:17.109 --> 01:18.140
Hey!

01:29.200 --> 01:31.019
Help me!

01:48.069 --> 01:49.159
At the warehouse.

01:51.120 --> 01:53.060
(whimpers)

02:19.050 --> 02:20.099
(switch clicks)

02:44.000 --> 02:45.090
Youre making it worse!

02:48.009 --> 02:49.110
(grunts)

03:16.079 --> 03:18.120
Landos dead. Shes gone.

03:18.129 --> 03:20.189
Shes too far developed.

03:23.219 --> 03:26.189
